{"tid":1431480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何強制家中電視唔播TVB","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:17:55.000Z","uid":277296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7833f4e2e54b9002d882240f2a110cd0fe155821","tid":1431480,"uid":277296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:07:53.000Z","msg":"最簡單當然係刪台/剪天線啦<br />\n但比人發現我相信你跳樓都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家教一個強制轉台既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先你要有三樣野<br />\n1)轉台神器<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjbSVo2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjbSVo2.jpg&h=8c47c4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2)一部唔用既後備電話<br />\n3)一部電腦/另一部電話<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n之後係部後備電話安裝TeamViewer QuickSupport及轉台App<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.teamviewer.quicksupport.market\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.teamviewer.quicksupport.market&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=35f03c52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.teamviewer.quicksupport.market</a><br />\n<br />\n再係主電話安裝TeamViewer遠端控制版本/電腦安裝Teamviewer<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.teamviewer.teamviewer.market.mobile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.teamviewer.teamviewer.market.mobile&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=04227e84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.teamviewer.teamviewer.market.mobile</a><br />\n由主電話/電腦 Remote 控制後備機轉台<br />\n你個人係公司/房都可以做到轉台師，配合Web Cam使用效果更佳! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6379dcd77bd45a1b26846fa3802999457e9fe01f","tid":1431480,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1i2yto.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1i2yto.png&h=266d33ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RZ5we3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RZ5we3.png&h=94b36a59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qWCyE8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqWCyE8o.jpg&h=7004c28d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YrRrZ8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYrRrZ8o.jpg&h=4251a037&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}